**__The U__**<span style="color: #a6a6a6; font-size: 6pt;">nited </span>**__N__**<span style="color: #a6a6a6; font-size: 6pt;">ations </span>**__Charter, like most__**<span style="color: #a6a6a6; font-size: 6pt;"> multilateral </span>**__treaties, binds only signatory states; it has no direct application to private actors. Therefore,__**<span style="color: #a6a6a6; font-size: 6pt;"> Article 2(4)’s </span>**__prohibition on__**<span style="color: #a6a6a6; font-size: 6pt;"> the use of </span>**__force applies only to states.__**



