rce">**<span style="color: #a6a6a6; font-size: 6pt;"> whose </span>**</span><span style="color: #a6a6a6; font-size: 6pt;">charisma</span><span style="font-size: 6pt;"> and organizational skills keep a group together. </span><span class="ReadSource">If</span><span style="font-size: 6pt;"> they </span>**__[leaders] are eliminated, they are__**<span class="ReadSource"> not easily replaced.</span><span style="font-size: 6pt;">18 Shikaki of the Islamic Jihad falls into this category.</span>

