Watch.__**<span style="color: #a6a6a6; font-size: 6pt;">39 The U.S. must counter this position by doing more to promote the legitimacy of the policy. The U.S. must articulate the policy’s legal and moral bases to our international partners and the public-at-large and push for a formal updating of jus in bello to reflect a state’s legitimate right to defend itself against trans- national terrorism.</span>


